  <div id="about" class="hidden">
    <div class="lead">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
            <p>Failure to effectively reach members of Congress has disastrous consequences. Studies show that politicians <a href="http://www.vanderbilt.edu/csdi/miller-stokes/08_MillerStokes_BroockmanSkovron.pdf"> fundamentally misconceive</a> their constituents&rsquo; views, making it harder for them to represent us in the lawmaking process.</p>
            <p>That&rsquo;s why we built Democracy.io: a new tool to put you in touch with your members of Congress&mdash;with as few clicks as possible.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
